MadWimax: INSTALL

These are the essential steps for compiling and installing this
software.

Prerequisites
-------------

 * Linux kernel with TUN/TAP support
 * libusb-1.0 (http://libusb.wiki.sourceforge.net/Libusb1.0)

Compiling
---------

Run 'make'.

Installing
----------

Copy the resulting binary to whereever you want :).

